r vacation gone all-too-predictably wrong. From beach bonfires to the search for Moby Trout, the mythical monster fish of Cornflower Lake, this novel is for anyone who’s spent a disappointing day at the beach.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 0aMasseursvFiction. 0aResortsvFiction. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / General.2bisacsh  aOkanagan, Okanagan resort.  aPostcard.  abad family vacation book.  abad vacation.  abeach book.  abeach holiday.  abeach read.  abeach.  acontemporary beach.  acontemporary fiction.  acontemporary womens fiction.  adaughter.  adenial.  adysfunctional.  afamily.  afather.  agetaways.  agift mother.  agifts for friend.  agifts for her.  agifts for mom.  ahappiness.  aholiday.  ahumour.  alake.  aliterary fiction.  aliterary humour.  amarriage.  amassage therapist.  amassage therapy.  amother.  apool.  aresort.  asearch for happiness.  ason.  asummer book.  asummer holiday.  asummer read.  asummer.  atrouble in paradise.  avacation gone wrong.  avacation.  awomen fiction.  awomens lives.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Complete eBook-Package 2021z978311127221408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2021z978311127464540uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9781773852171?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781773852171423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781773852171/original  a978-3-11-127221-4  ACUP Complete eBook-Package 2021b2021  a978-3-11-127464-5  ACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2021b2021  aGBV-deGruyter-alles